[{"ave_id":"AVE-2008-0002","file_name":"2008/AVE-2008-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2008-1059","title":"WordPress Sniplets 插件远程文件包含漏洞","description":"WordPress 的 Sniplets 插件 1.1.2 及 1.2.2 版本中存在 PHP 远程文件包含漏洞，位于 `modules/syntax_highlight.php` 文件中。未经认证的远程攻击者可通过 `libpath` 参数传入恶意 URL，导致任意 PHP 代码执行。攻击者可利用此漏洞完全控制目标网站服务器，危害严重。受影响的用户应立即升级或禁用该插件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2008-1059"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2008-02-28T19:44:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:50:53.943","remediation":"立即停用并彻底删除 Sniplets 插件（1.1.2/1.2.2 版），该插件已停止维护，无安全更新。如必须使用，修改 php.ini 中 allow_url_include 和 allow_url_fopen 为 Off，并升级 WordPress 至最新版本以减缓攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/29099","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/3706","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/488734/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/27985","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/40829","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/5194","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-1059.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-1059.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2008/CVE-2008-1059.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6b5bb884a1dbb91134673e92ed8e62094db574f9/cves/2008/1xxx/CVE-2008-1059.json","https://github.com/topscoder/nuclei-wordfence-cve/blob/b4db95253d9e0f4fa88894d49422458d88bb2c32/nuclei-templates/2008/CVE-2008-1059-sniplets-5e90704e-1a0c-448c-9139-542927cfa4f8.yaml","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2008/README.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2008-1059_2.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/a5ed01398c096830b618c734267e2ea50e3a69c5/2008/CVE-2008-1059.json","