logies 已于 2008 年发布修复版本）。当前仍在使用的应迁移至受支持的 Titan MFT 或 Titan SFTP 产品线。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面限制对 TCP 端口 21 的访问，仅允许白名单 IP 连接；同时在 IPS/IDS 设备上添加规则，检测并拦截长度超过 1024 字节的 USER 或 PASS 命令参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/28760","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/3639","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/487431/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/27568","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2008/0393","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/5036","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2008/CVE-2008-0702.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2008/CVE-2008-0702.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/network/cves/2008/CVE-2008-0702.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2008/0xxx/CVE-2008-0702.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2008/CVE-2008-0702","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2008-0702_6.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/network/cves/2008/CVE-2008-0702.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2008/CVE-2008-0702.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/179c45b9fa0538b72b0d380b72ed3445aca781eb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-m434-vxwp-c3vg/GHSA-m434-vxwp-c3vg.json","https://github.com/tholian-network/vulnerabilities/blob/cd8798a37e6d58633681c9596bee14e4189ad0e9/database/vulnerability/CVE-2008-0702.json","https://github.com/sailuh/perceive/blob/85ca622832e25fa91d8d836b8c93a096178bb35d/Notebooks/NVD/data/2008.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"